************************************************************

The Official AMOS Club
***********************

SeaScape Software is now authorised by the Official AMOS 
Club, to accept memberships for the Official AMOS Club in 
the UK.  A subscription to the AMOS Club is $29.95 Cdn (for 
Canadian residents), or $29.95 US (for American residents).  
Every two months you will receive a 20-page newsletter, 
packed full of AMOS information for beginners and experts 
alike.  

The following products are available to AMOS Club members 
only:

1. The Disk (AMOS Club Newsletter companion disk) 

   6 issue subscription (one every two months) - DOES NOT 
   REPLACE the newsletter.  "The Disk" is the optional AMOS 
   Newsletter disk for AMOS Club members.  It contains all 
   the source code of each newsletter, required graphics, 
   10-liners, utilities, examples, etc.  Back issues are 
   always available.

   price: $19.95 Cdn (for Canadian residents), or $19.95 US   
          (for American residents).

2. CText 2.5

   price: $23.95 Cdn (for Canadian residents), or $23.95 US   
          (for American residents).

3. Sprite X 3.0

   price: $29.95 Cdn (for Canadian residents), or $29.95 US   
          (for American residents).



The following products are available to AMOS Club members, 
and non-AMOS Club members:

1. AMOS TOME Series IV

   AMOS TOME is the ultimate extension for AMOS.  AMOS TOME   
   Series IV comes with 67 commands, TOME Editor, 4 demo      
   games (with sourcecode), 80 page manual, and example 
   programs for all the commands.  AMOS TOME works with AMOS
   1.34, 1.36, and the AMOS Compiler.  It also works with     
   all Amigas, including the Amiga 1200 and 4000.

   price: $49.95 Cdn (for Canadian residents), or $49.95 US
          (for American residents).  FOR AMOS CLUB MEMBERS!

          $59.95 Cdn (for Canadian residents), or $59.95 US
          (for American residents).  FOR NON-AMOS CLUB 
          MEMBERS!

2. AMOS TOME Goodies Disks

   price: $9.95 Cdn (for Canadian residents), or $9.95 US
          (for American residents).

SeaScape Software accepts bank/postal money orders, cash 
(store only), cheques, and MasterCard (store only).  

Amiga Manitoba User Group (AMUG) members receive 5% off of 
the prices listed above.

